Kestrel Retains Its Rank as Kenya’s Biggest Brokerage, Business Daily Says

-- B y   P a u l   R i c h a r d s o n
-- 
2011-04-01T04:23:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-01/kestrel-retains-its-rank-as-kenya-s-biggest-brokerage-business-daily-says.html
Kestrel Capital (East Africa) Ltd.
retained its rank as  Kenya ’s biggest stock brokerage by market
share, Business Daily reported, citing annual reports.  Kestrel has a market share of 19 percent, while Dyer &
Blair Investment Bank ranks second with 12 percent, the Nairobi-
based newspaper said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Richardson at 
 pmrichardson@bloomberg.net  